{"id":125,"date":"2025-05-24T14:34:55","date_gmt":"2025-05-24T14:34:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/?page_id=125"},"modified":"2025-05-25T17:48:18","modified_gmt":"2025-05-25T17:48:18","slug":"philosophy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/philosophy\/","title":{"rendered":"Philosophy"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"125\" class=\"elementor elementor-125\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-544a58ee elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-top elementor-section-content-top elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"544a58ee\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-71f243d1\" data-id=\"71f243d1\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-978e744 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"978e744\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a9ff4a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2a9ff4a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05d031e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"05d031e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9b406f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c9b406f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"comp-js73jm1r\" class=\"HcOXKn SxM0TO QxJLC3 lq2cno YQcXTT comp-js73jm1r wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\"><h2 class=\"font_2 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">The Philosophy of Our Practice<\/span><\/h2><\/div><div id=\"comp-js73jm1x\" class=\"HcOXKn c9GqVL QxJLC3 lq2cno YQcXTT comp-js73jm1x wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">The hallmark of our philosophy is asking (and reevaluating throughout the representation of the client)<\/span><\/p><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">\u200b<\/span><\/span><\/p><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Four Basic Questions:<\/span><\/p><ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">What is the objective to be achieved?<\/span><\/p><\/li><li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Is litigation the most effective way to achieve it?<\/span><\/p><\/li><li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Is the cost of litigation (both financial and otherwise) justified by the potential reward? and<\/span><\/p><\/li><li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">If litigation is the answer, what specific litigation steps will most effectively achieve the desired result?<\/span><\/p><\/li><\/ul><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">\u200b<\/span><\/span><\/p><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">The goal in other words, is not litigation for litigation&#8217;s sake; we have frequently advised clients that their interests would be best served by not initiating litigation and instead exploring an alternative way to resolve their dispute. Whether or not you retain our Firm, we urge you to ask (and re-ask on a periodic basis) these four questions of your attorney throughout the representation.<\/span><\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-561c86f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"561c86f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1de738c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1de738c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2016\" height=\"1344\" src=\"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/LAW-FIRM-PHOTO.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-134\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/LAW-FIRM-PHOTO.jpg 2016w, https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/LAW-FIRM-PHOTO-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/LAW-FIRM-PHOTO-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/LAW-FIRM-PHOTO-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/LAW-FIRM-PHOTO-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2016px) 100vw, 2016px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75412da e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"75412da\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f23a0d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9f23a0d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1c2194 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a1c2194\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Law-firms.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-75\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Law-firms.jpeg 900w, https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Law-firms-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Law-firms-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1395795 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1395795\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3ca9010 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3ca9010\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"comp-js73snbt\" class=\"HcOXKn SxM0TO QxJLC3 lq2cno YQcXTT comp-js73snbt wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\"><h2 class=\"font_2 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"color_26 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Clients&#8217; Input<\/span><\/span><\/h2><\/div><div id=\"WRchTxtc-14xk\" class=\"HcOXKn c9GqVL QxJLC3 lq2cno YQcXTT WRchTxtc-14xk wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"color_26 wixui-rich-text__text\">We have come to understand, after more than forty years of practice, that clients (as the individuals with the most direct knowledge of the facts and the persons most immediately impacted by the dispute) very often have valuable insights and suggestions about how the litigation or a transaction should be conducted. \u00a0Far too many attorneys treat clients and their concerns as an inconvenience and necessary evil of the practice of law; we never do. \u00a0For that reason, we always return client emails and telephone calls promptly and consider all client suggestions and comments.<\/span><\/span><\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1de2d2f5 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1de2d2f5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7f112c2d\" data-id=\"7f112c2d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dbde371 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dbde371\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"comp-js741a29\" class=\"HcOXKn SxM0TO QxJLC3 lq2cno YQcXTT comp-js741a29 wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\"><h2 class=\"font_2 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"color_26 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">A Word About Size<\/span><\/span><\/h2><\/div><div id=\"comp-js741a2a\" class=\"HcOXKn c9GqVL QxJLC3 lq2cno YQcXTT comp-js741a2a wixui-rich-text\" data-testid=\"richTextElement\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"color_26 wixui-rich-text__text\">Clients are sometimes concerned about retaining a small firm when the opposing party may be represented by a much larger firm. \u00a0For a number of reasons, we have always considered our rather modest size as an advantage, rather than as a liability. \u00a0For one thing, a small firm results in significantly reduced legal fees for the client; we simply do not have layers of lawyers to assign as a &#8220;team&#8221; to a matter. \u00a0Second, because there is no hierarchy at the Firm, the &#8220;partners in charge&#8221; (Mr. Feit and\/or Mr. Blander) do everything and know everything about the case. In the rare instances when it is necessary (such as a case with heavy document review), we retain contract attorneys to assist us with these discrete tasks under our supervision (which also represents a potential substantial cost savings to the client).<\/span><\/span><\/p><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">\u200b<\/span><\/p><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"color_26 wixui-rich-text__text\">To be sure, neither of these advantages would matter if we were unable to effectively litigate and protect the interests of our clients. \u00a0But this has never been a problem. Indeed, in a substantial portion of our cases, our adversary is significantly larger and is often a &#8220;national law firm&#8221; (with hundreds, if not thousands, of attorneys). \u00a0To put it bluntly, the issue is not the number of attorneys who go to court, work on a deal or prepare the brief. \u00a0Rather, it is the quality of the product and the representation, which is a function of the intelligence, dedication, experience, creativity and hard work of the attorney involved.<\/span><\/span><\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Philosophy of Our Practice The hallmark of our philosophy is asking (and reevaluating throughout the representation of the client) \u200b Four Basic Questions: What is the objective to be achieved? Is litigation the most effective way to achieve it? Is the cost of litigation (both financial and otherwise) justified by the potential reward? and [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"pagelayer_contact_templates":[],"_pagelayer_content":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-125","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/125","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=125"}],"version-history":[{"count":28,"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/125\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":346,"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/125\/revisions\/346"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/labonteandassociates.com\/hhand\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=125"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}